{"tid":2209589,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"收費做黃圈認證點睇？","createTime":"2020-09-19T18:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T02:04:26.000Z","uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21cc3404dc7ed569a23f595e7a03460affbb093f","tid":2209589,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:02:38.000Z","msg":"大多假黃店，貼哂連豬都可以係食人血饅頭。<br />\n如果係咁，不如直接賣黃圈認證，起碼就算係偽黃，佢都比左錢買認證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>權威性</ins><br />\n要有民運人士支持，保證到啲錢係安全咁去到手足手上<br />\n<br />\n<ins>防偽</ins><br />\nQR code 連去認證機構網站，顯示店名同地址<br />\n<br />\n<ins>法律</ins><br />\n唔可以用支助手足做認證目的，可以用食物質素，食品安全，環保之類<br />\n<br />\n<ins>設計</ins><br />\n唔好再用連豬，試下design個認真少少logo, 細細張，唔好咁顯眼，低調啲，比手足識別到就得。<br />\n唔洗下下拎個喇叭岀黎同人講自己係黃<br />\n<br />\n<ins>等級</ins><br />\n要分唔同等級，除左捐款多少，仲要考慮埋表態，行動。等手足大概知你有幾黃<br />\n<br />\n<ins>缺點</ins><br />\n中心化左，做唔到be water, 會形成後台，証證人權力過大。"},{"pid":"18cc44592751b887babd5022557ab1c5b2b2bec6","tid":2209589,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"唔太認同, 一有大台就比港共集中擊破"},{"pid":"7d5c560169d4f61d8c6ccac1bb11c1e8773d7e43","tid":2209589,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"Sorry 不過真係唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一同錢掛鈎就有10萬個方法瓦解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a057f4e4a3bb4ec10a964f79ecee744665af1e","tid":2209589,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"其實我唔覺得身邊好多假黃店"},{"pid":"77bb2006c8960dc57a977675c13748a82523a5a7","tid":2209589,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:22:14.000Z","msg":"又嚟<br />\n之前有人試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519b7b6d15e2cce6d0fca423d996259f109ade5e","tid":2209589,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"